OOC at bottom.

::KitKat2/StarScream::

KitKat gets up from the table in the mess hall.
"I'm gonna go find DrillBit. They should still be planing on how to get
DarkFate back."

StarScream gets up as well, after finishing his energon drink.
"I'll come along," he says.

KitKat checks the computer and sees that DrillBit is with Killfest and
Shivia and others at an equipment room.

"Lets go," says KitKat2. 

Her and StarScream head off in that direction.

OOC: Welcome back. It's always nice to be able to RP with you logo!
Nothing much has changed with the Predacons. They are at BlackFortress.
DrillBit still leads with Killfest and DarkFate. DrillBit and KitKat2
are not married yet.(sigh) Currently DarkFate is captured by one of the
enemy factions.(Who has him anyway, Airly? I forgot.) And SilverScout is
running around BlackFortress while we try to capture her. You wont be
able to get into BF right away, because all the defences are up, and the
base is covered in lava right now.
